ğŸ“– Project Description

This is a simple Todo List Web Application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
It allows users to easily add, edit, and delete tasks, helping them stay organized and productive.
The app dynamically updates the list and saves tasks in the browserâ€™s memory (if localStorage is used), ensuring that tasks remain even after refreshing the page.

