ğŸ§  Concepts Used

This project demonstrates key JavaScript fundamentals covered in the tutorial videos, including:

DOM manipulation (document.querySelector, addEventListener, etc.)

Event handling (adding, editing, deleting tasks)

Array methods and loops

Conditional statements

Function creation and reuse

Optional: Local storage to save tasks

ğŸ§© How to Run the Project

