Simply open the index.html file in your web browser.

ğŸ§ª Testing the Application

The application was tested to ensure all features work correctly:

Users can successfully add a new task.

Tasks can be edited and updated in place.

Tasks can be deleted and removed from the list.

All UI updates occur instantly without page reload.



